Program: Outlook
Title: South African Fruit Picker Challenges Tesco
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbsd2
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
South African fruit picker, Gertruida Baartman attends the AGM of British supermarket chain, Tesco to campaign for better pay. Inspiration for the novel 'The Bookseller of Kabul', Shah Mohammed Rais brings case against the author. Part 2 of Nick Clarke's Cancer audio diary.